data.title: Taxonomic Classification of Phylum Echinodermata PDF
data.meta_description: Taxonomic Classification of Phylum Echinodermata PDF - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document outlines the taxonomic classification of the phylum Echinodermata, which includes classes such as Asteroidea, Ophiuroidea, Echinoidea, and Holothuroidea. It lists examples of orders and species within each class, including starfish, brittle stars, sea urchins, and sea cucumbers.
